# PayPal API keys — put your Live Client ID on line 1, Secret on line 2.
# Get them: https://developer.paypal.com/dashboard/applications
# Enable "Transaction Search" on the app. Do not commit this file.
#
# Format A (easiest):
#   YOUR_CLIENT_ID_HERE
#   YOUR_CLIENT_SECRET_HERE
#
# Format B:
#   CLIENT_ID=...
#   CLIENT_SECRET=...
#   MODE=live

PASTE_CLIENT_ID_HERE
PASTE_CLIENT_SECRET_HERE
